  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb5\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is no change in the stand that Podujana Peramuna will support Ranil - Sagara Kariyavasam",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "There is no change in the announcement that Budujana Peramuna will support the acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "My declaration will surely succeed. Sagara Kariyawasam, Secretary General of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna said that most members of Podujana Peramuna will support the President in the presidential election.",
        "Budhil mentioned the above when asked about the position of Podujana Peramuna regarding providing support to Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The political leadership must first accept that the country is facing a massive economic crisis.",
        "A one-party plan for economic recovery and regime change is consistently ignored. The government has changed several times in the past six months but the issues have not been resolved.",
        "After the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, Ranil Wickramasinghe was appointed as Acting President. We decided to support Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe in the vote for the presidential election to be held in Parliament the day after tomorrow, so that the problems found in the social structure should be at least partially resolved.",
        "There is no change in the decision to support Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe. My announcement will definitely succeed. Most members of Podujana Peramuna will support Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Those who demand a solution from the economic crisis should cooperate with the projects implemented for economic recovery. Answer The projects carried out under the leadership of President Ranil Wickremesinghe are seen as a solution to the current crisis.",
        "We clearly note that there are huge differences between him and our party in terms of political principles."
      ],
